yingyinNormal.en: Commander, I have an idea. Go ahead, Mark.
yingyinNormal.zh: 指挥官，我有个点子。说吧，马克。

yingyinNormal.en: He was commander of the Autobots before me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他曾是汽车人的指挥官，是我的前任。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I don't intend to be like every other commander.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没打算和别的指挥官一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, who's troops do you propose as a decoy, Commander.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哪个军队要作为诱饵呢，指挥官。

yingyinNormal.en: Attention! Officer on deck! Hey, Bean. Ho, Commander!
yingyinNormal.zh: 立正，长官巡视甲板。嘿，小豆子。你好，指挥官。

yingyinNormal.en: Anduin, stop! You killed him! Commander. Please, sir. Please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 安度因，停下！你害死了他！指挥官。不要这样，长官。不要这样。

yingyinNormal.en: Signed, Brigadier General Musgrove. War Services Commander, Washington DC.
yingyinNormal.zh: 签署，准将穆斯格罗夫，战争服务指挥官，华盛顿特区。

yingyinNormal.en: Vogel. Go ahead, Commander. I need you to come inside and make a bomb. Again, Commander?
yingyinNormal.zh: 沃格尔，说吧，指挥官，我想你回来做一个炸弹。你说什么，指挥官？

yingyinNormal.en: Ender. Every other commander has their seniors closest to the door.
yingyinNormal.zh: 安德，别的指挥官都让老兵睡在靠门的一边。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm commander Paylor of District 8. I'm a soldier like all of you, so...
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是第八区的指挥官佩勒，与你们一样，我也是名战士，所以…

yingyinNormal.en: Salaam, Alai. Salaam, Commander! Bernard. Good to see you, sir. At ease.
yingyinNormal.zh: 日安，阿莱。日安，指挥官。伯纳德。很高兴见到你，长官。稍息。

yingyinNormal.en: Commander Paylor. Your people, have suffered more than just as anyone else in the hands of the Capitol.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩勒指挥官，你的军队是与国会区交手最多的。

yingyinNormal.en: Step forward please. This is commander Spock. He is one of our most distinguished graduates.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请到前面来，这位是史波克指挥官，是我们的优秀毕业生。

yingyinNormal.en: Their very existence is a threat. Is that clear, Commander? Clear, sir. Good. Carry on, Colonel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们的存在就是个威胁，明白吗，指挥官？明白，很好，请继续，上校。

yingyinNormal.en: We don't have to make it, Bruce. He does. Yeah. But, bullshit. Should be Commander Lewis' call.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不用抉择，布鲁斯，他来。是啊，但是废话，应该让路易斯指挥官来决定。

yingyinNormal.en: In a matter of weeks, we may be called on to fight a real battle. Let's bring your commander up to speed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大约几周内我们可能被调派去一场真实的战争，我们来帮指挥官跟上进度吧。

yingyinNormal.en: For the love of God. This is a joke, obviously. I'm afraid I don't know what those are, Commander Denniston.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的天呐！显然，这就是个笑话。恐怕我不知道什么是笑话，丹尼斯顿指挥官。

yingyinNormal.en: I've scoured every single data file on Commander Lewis personal drive. This is officially the least disco song she owns.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我把路易斯指挥官个人硬盘的每一个文件都翻了一遍，这真真儿是她最不迪斯科的歌了。

yingyinNormal.en: Commander Denniston, Royal Navy. All right, Mr. Turing, I'll bite. Why do you wish to work for His Majesty's government? Oh, I don't, really.
yingyinNormal.zh: 丹尼斯顿指挥官，皇家海军。好吧，图灵先生，我服了你了。你为什么想为政府工作？哦，其实，我真的不想。
